-*- outline -*-

This is the dlvhex-KBMod ActionAddon, an addon for 'dlvhex-actionplugin'.

This file contains information on compiling and installing and using the 
rdfplugin.

* Dependencies
dlvhex-KBMod ActionAddon depends on the following:

** dlvhex
http://www.kr.tuwien.ac.at/staff/roman/dlvhex/


* Building the dlvhex-KBMod ActionAddon

** Prerequisites

*** dlvhex
See dlvhex installation instructions at:
http://con.fusion.at/dlvhex/download.php

** Building

The typical procedure to build is:

./configure
make
make install

Some more information for each step follows:

*** Configuration

`./configure --enable-userinstall' will instal the addon to the users home
folder i.e.`~/.dlvhex/plugins'. By default the addon will be installed
in the DLVPATH/lib/dlvhex/plugins.

General configuration options and explanation of related environment variables
can be found using
`./configure --help'

** Installation
Run `make install' to install dlvhex-KBMod ActionAddon into a system-wide
plugin directory provided by dlvhex.
